  "3266530": {
    "name": "Diorama Builder - Secret Bunker",
    "steam_appid": 3266530,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266530/extras/bcbfb32273a138b305a27f6da467bff7.avif?t=1750890882\" width=616 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个扩展到 <strong>西洋镜建设者</strong> 的功能是 &quot;<u><strong>秘密碉堡</strong></u>&quot;, 它将允许您设置一个地下超级碉堡. 例如, 您可以在其中设置电梯, 将探索巴士运送到地面, 为居民提供完整的健身房, 大型宿舍 厨房和自助餐厅, 以及控制室和通信室等!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>部件数量 \\ 系列的数量</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266530/extras/a27aa92bb9ba65602c8d6349df57c75b.webp?t=1750890882\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >下面我们将介绍玩家在这个西洋镜中设置的场景的一些细节: </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>车库电梯</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266530/extras/7022e709b727c3859156b6a762388892.poster.avif?t=1750890882\" width=616 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266530/extras/7022e709b727c3859156b6a762388892.webm?t=1750890882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266530/extras/7022e709b727c3859156b6a762388892.mp4?t=1750890882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >电梯负责将外部探险巴士从地面运输到地下碉堡, 反之亦然. 在这些外出探险, 团队带回供应品来补给碉堡的居民. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>控制室</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266530/extras/6673c368884d5bf4ba0b2a6258b8a764.poster.avif?t=1750890882\" width=616 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266530/extras/6673c368884d5bf4ba0b2a6258b8a764.webm?t=1750890882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266530/extras/6673c368884d5bf4ba0b2a6258b8a764.mp4?t=1750890882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在控制室中, 所有通信都与外部和内部进行 (通过在所有环境中找到的扬声器), 并进行表面分析和对所有燃油操作和机械的控制. 这里是控制碉堡运行所需的物资和产品库存, 空气质量和其他信息的地方. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >健身房</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266530/extras/e6d78e2b24db48d49158745672f43d62.poster.avif?t=1750890882\" width=616 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266530/extras/e6d78e2b24db48d49158745672f43d62.webm?t=1750890882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266530/extras/e6d78e2b24db48d49158745672f43d62.mp4?t=1750890882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >健身房非常多样化, 拥有各种设备和资源, 以便地堡中的居民可以锻炼和训练自卫能力, 以应对迫在眉睫的危险情况, 例如外部入侵! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>种植园</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266530/extras/7f8aec168edd94925afb28f76fbaee35.poster.avif?t=1750890882\" width=616 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266530/extras/7f8aec168edd94925afb28f76fbaee35.webm?t=1750890882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266530/extras/7f8aec168edd94925afb28f76fbaee35.mp4?t=1750890882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >种植园用于种植各种蔬菜, 以喂养碉堡的居民. 整个过程包括灌溉, 施肥和护理, 以确保这些基本成分始终能够满足该团体的食物需求. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与 西洋镜建 中的所有其他<strong>西洋镜建设者</strong>一样:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本模型的音乐也是专门制作的 <strong>原创音乐</strong>. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成模型后, 场景中的动画将自动激活, <strong>互动模式</strong>,也将激活, 您可以通过点击不同的预定义位置与场景进行互动, 观看非常酷的动画. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 <strong>互动模式</strong>中, 您可以激活<strong>夜间模式</strong>, 同时打开所有场景灯, 从而能够欣赏到非常特别的西洋镜图. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将有新的 <strong>成就</strong> 等你来解锁!</p></li></ul>",
